Algeria: Mutuwar Mahmoud Guemama - Algeria Ta Rasa Wani Patriot, Wani Da Ya Yi Alkawari, In Ji Shugaban Tebboune.
Algiers - Shugaban Kasa, Abdelmadjid Tebboune, ya aika wata sakonin tausayi ga 'yan majalisar jama'ar kasa (APN), Mujahed Mahmoud Guemama, wanda ya rasu Litinin, inda ya ce Algeria "ta rasa wani jinin kasa da wani yan kasa da ya yi kokarin ganin ayyukan jama'arsa da kasarsa."
Algeria ta rasa yau, ta yawan mutuwar Mujahed Mahmoud Guemama, wani yan kishin al'umma da kasa, wani mutum wanda bai taba yin watsi da adalci ba, kuma ya kasance mai tabbatar da adalci daga lokacin da ya fara yin harkokin Mujahedeen tare da abokan arzikinsa har zuwa lokacin da ya mutu a ranar da muke cikin takaici, shugaban Tebboune ya rubuta cikin saƙon ta'aziyyarsa.
"Mahmoud Guemama, Allah ya yi masa rahama, ya kasance daga cikin wata tsohuwar shekara ta masu yin adalci da kalubale don kasar su, wadanda suka yi wa kansu rahusa don kasar su," in ji shugaban kasa.
"Mutumin da ya rasu ya yi rayuwarsa ta kare kasar Aljeriya daga cin zarafin kolonialism na kasa da kasa, ta shiga cikin juyin mulkin yakin neman gaskiya a shekarar 1960 a taron koyarwa na Tahart na wulaya ta tarihi ta VI."
Shugaban da ya wuce ya sanannu ne ga dukkaninmu saboda tabbacin da ya nuna na kishin sojoji da kuma alfahari da ya yi wajen tabbatar da hoton al'ummar Aljeriya mai arziki da kuma hadin kai, in ji Shugaban Tebboune.
A cikin kasashen yamma maso gabas, late Mahmoud Guemama yana da kyakkyawan suna a matsayin wanda ke tsakanin yaki, yana shiga tsakanin 'yan'uwa a cikin kasar da ke da yanayi idan an kunna wuta ta yaki, Shugaban ya kara a cikin sajensa.
"Dukkan wadannan siffofi da kima sun samar da late Mahmoud Guemama ƙarfin gwiwa da aminci daga mutanen Tamanrasset wadanda suka zaba shi don ya riƙa ƙunsar su a Majalisar Mutane ta Kasa (APN) a yanayi da yawa, lokacin da ya zama sakataren kasashen yankin da kuma ƴan uwansa, har ma ya zama wakilin kuma ɗan sanda ga dukkan aljeriyawa," ya rubuta Shugaban Kasa.
Baƙin ciki ba zai isa ya yi wa mujahed Mahmoud Guemama, amininsa, adalci ba.
Ya tafi mu yau a lokacin da Aljeriya ta bukata shi," in ji shugaban.
