Majalisar birnin Kansas City ta yabawa taimakon federal a magance yaduwar mutuwa, amma ta tsorata dalilin da Trump ke bi.
Majalisar Birnin Kansas City, Quinton Lucas, ya tambaye a ranar Lahadi game da nufin da Shugaban Kasa Trump ya aika da 'yan sanda zuwa birane na Amurka - yana cewa, yayin da zai amince da taimakon wajen warware yawan kisan da suka faru a birnin tekun na Midwest, ya gaskata cewa wannan mataki zai iya zama game da tabbatar da zaben sake zama na Trump.
Lucas, wanda ya ke jam'iyyar Dimokradiyya, ya ce a ranar Lahadi a kan talabijin Fox News, cewa ya yi mamaki da yadda shugaban ya ambaci bikin nuna goyon bayan George Floyd da kuma kungiyar Black Lives Matter, bayan bikin da ya faru akan rashin adalci da sata da sojoji.
A ba haka a Kansas City ba. Mun samu karuwar shekaru-a-shekaru amma abin da muke bukata shi ne taimakon wajen gano wasu daga cikin mazauna bata da gaskiya.
Lucas ya kara da cewa: "Muna yi kokarin samun wani tsokaci da zai zama mai tsayayya akan magance kisan kai... Ina ganin idan ku saurari bayanai da aka fitar a gabannin lokaci... muna farin ciki da aiki tare da jami'an tsaron federal a cikin wani yanki da ya dace."
Duk da yanayin nasa na yin aiki tare da hukumar tsaro ta jihar, Lucas ya ce maganganun Trump - musamman a yayin da ya shiga cikin tashin hankali game da hanyoyin da aka yi amfani da su a Portland, Ore., da hukumar tsaro ta federal - ya sa yawan mutane daga cikin masu zabe masa suka yi magana game da halin da hukumar tsaro take a cikin birane.
Ya ce, "Abin da ba mu bukata shi ne mafi yawan mai a wuta daga jami'an tsaron federal don yin, na gaskata, wani batu na siyasa mai ban mamaki."
Ranar Litinin, Trump ya sanar da cewa yana aika 100 'yan sanda na federal zuwa Chicago don taimakawa wajen yaki da karuwar yawan wasu laifuka - wannan mataki yana nuna ci gaba da shigar da White House cikin tsaro na yankin da Trump ke ci gaba da sanya kansa a matsayin shugaban tsaro da kariya.
"Surge" na masu aiki da aka sanar a ranar Laraba zuwa Chicago da sauran birane a Amurka, shine ɗayan tsarin Operation Legend - wanda aka sanya sunansa bayan LeGend Taliferro, wanda ya mutu yayin da yake bacci a cikin gidan apartment a Kansas City a ƙarshen wata baya.
Yayin da ake aika da masu aikin gwamnati don taimakawa da hukumar tsaro ta yankin ba abu mai ban mamaki bane - Shugaban Kasa Bill Barr ya sanar da wani nufin karuwa a watan Disamba ga birane guda bakwai da suka samu karuwar zaman lafiya - irin masu aikin gwamnati da ake aika da su, da wasu hanyoyinsu, sun tabbatar da cewa an yi taka tsantsan tsakanin shugabannin yankin da na jihar.
Gwamnonin doka daga New York zuwa Portland sun yi magana a kan aikin Trump na aika masu aikin gwamnati zuwa biranen su, musamman bayan rahoton cewa masu aikin gwamnati ba a sani ba sun tsare makiyaya a Portland kuma suka kai su cikin motocin da ba a sani ba.
Portland ta samu yawan zanga-zangar kullum akan rashin adalci da rikici tsakanin al'umma tun bayan mutuwar George Floyd a cikin hannun 'yan sanda na Minneapolis a ranar 25 ga watan Mayu.
