Ted Cruz ya ce manufofin Pelosi suna "shoveling kudi akan matsalar kuma kashe Amurka"
Washington - Senator Ted Cruz na Republican daga Texas ya zargi Speaker Nancy Pelosi da House Democrats da neman wani kayan aiki na coronavirus da ya kunshi "shoveling kudi akan matsalar kuma rufe Amurka" yayin da harkokin yin magana akan matakin gaba na ci gaba.
A cikin wata tattaunawa da "Fuskanci Al'umma" a Laraba, Cruz ya ce kasar ta fuskanci biyu matsaloli a tare: wata cutar da ta kashe rayukan mutane fiye da 600,000 a duniya da kuma wata "tsarin tattalin arziki mai tsanani" a Amurka.
Cruz ya ce Pelosi, wanda ta bayyana a "Fuskanci Alkawari" kafin senetar, "ba ta kula da kowane daga cikin wadannan ba".
Hausa: Ya ce Texas Republican, "Tasirin da take so ta yi shi ne, ta yi kokarin shigar da kudi a matsalar kuma ta kashe Amurka."
Kuma wani abu mai kyau, ku duba $3 trillion kudin da take neman saukarwa, wannan kawai yana kawo kudi ga abokan ta ba tare da magance matsalar ba. Manufarmu ya kamata ne mutane masu zaman kansu su dawo aiki. Suna so su iya samar da abinci ga iyalinsu.
Senate masu mulki da White House sun yi kwana biyu a kwanan nan yana tattaunawa kan sharuddan na tsarin magance cutar coronavirus na hudu, wanda suka sa ran zai kudin dala biliyan daya.
Yau da Asabar, Shugaban Ma'aikatar Gidan White House Mark Meadows da Ma'aikatar Kudi Steven Mnuchin sun koma Capitol Hill don tattaunawa da ma'aikatan Majalisar Dattawa, kuma Mnuchin ya gaya wa Fox News a wata tattaunawa da ta yi yau Lahadi cewa bayanai za a bayyana su ne ta hanyar Shugaban Majalisar Dattawa Mitch McConnell ranar Litinin.
Matsalar mafi muhimmanci ga masu yin sharadi - da kuma wani abu da ya zama abin takaici tsakanin Jam'iyyun Jamhuriyya da Jam'iyyar Dimokuradiyya - shine ƙarewar ƙarin albashi na aiki, wanda ya fara ɓacewa wannan Asabar.
Democrats suna so su kara kara "fage na hudu" na coronavirus package don kara $600 zuwa cikin albashi, amma Republicans suna kira don a rage shi kuma suka yi magana cewa wasu Amurka suna samun kudi fiye da yadda suka samu a aikin su.
Cruz ya ce fiye da haɗin rabin mutane a Amurka da suke samun sakamakon karuwar albashi suna samun kudi fiye da lokacin da suke aiki, kuma ya ce ya tattauna da masu kamfanoni masu yawa a Texas wadanda suke da wahala wajen sake dawo da ma'aikata.
Ya kamata ba su dawo ba saboda gwamnatin tarayya ta biya musu, a wasu yanayi, dubu biyu da yawa don su zauna gida," ya ce.
Cruz ya ce Majalisar Dattawa ta kamata ta yi kokarin yin wani shirin mayar da martani wanda zai sa saukin aiki ga Amurka ta hanyar sauke sakamako da dokoki a kan kananan kamfanoni: "babu kawai a cire trilioni daga kofar, wani shirin mayar da martani zai sauke sakamako na albashin aiki, wanda zai baiwa duk wanda ke aiki a Amurka karin albashin aiki. Wannan yana da tasiri wajen saukar da aiki." Ya ce.
Gwamnan Trump ya bukaci a kwanan nan cewa akwatin gudunmawa na gaba ya hada da kururin kudin shiga, amma Mnuchin ya ce ba zai zama part na dokar ba, saboda shawarar ta samu karancin karbuwa daga masu jam'iyyar Republican.
Mr. Trump ya yarda cewa kudin kudin albashin zai rasa daga sakonnin gaba daya amma ya nema ya aza laifin a kan Jam'iyyun Dimokuradiyya.
Cruz, wanda ya yi bakin ciki a kwanakin baya game da kudin da za a biya na kayan aiki na gaba, ya ce Asabar ba shi da goyon bayan wannan mataki daga kakannin sa na Majalisar Dattawa na Jamhuriyar Republican.
Ya kuma ya yi kira da bakin ciki ga wani kudin dala biliyan 3 da aka yi wa doka da majalisar da 'yan jam'iyyar jam'iyyar Dimokuradiyya a watan Mayu, kuma ya zargi 'yan takararsa da nufin yin wani abu da zai cutar da shugaban kafin zaben watan Nuwamba.
"Dukkanin manufar da jam'iyyar Dimokuradawa ke da shi shi ne su kawar da Donald Trump, kuma sun yanke shawarar cewa hanyar da za su kawar da shi ita ce su kashe dukkanin kamfanoni a Amurka, su kashe dukkanin makarantu a Amurka," ya ce.
