Review: Aeschylus ya bayyana halin nasara na zamanin da ta gabata a cikin 'The Persians'
A'a yawan aiki, kusan babu labari, a cikin "The Persians".
Mutane suna yin tafiya-tafiya, yana magana (da gaske mai tsanani) game da abubuwa (da gaske na tashin hankali) da suka faru a nesa.
Wannan shirin National Theater of Greece ya sanya fitar da muryar da take da karfi sosai.
A lokacin da yake cikin mafi karfi, shirin ya yi kama da wani rauni a cikin solar plexus, wanda ya hana ku hauwa - amfanin bai yi kasa ba idan aka kallo shi online.
An fara fitar da "The Persians" na Aeschylus a 472 B.C., an gano shi ne mafi tsofaffin wasan Girkan da ya rayu.
Wannan shirin Dimitris Lignadis ya fito ne a ranar Asabar daga teatocin tarihin Epidaurus; a cikin ruhin teatocin, babu wani rikodin da ya samu akan layi.
An fara tunani da wurin ne saboda yana cikin asclepeion (wurin magani) na birni saboda yadda Yunawa suka yi tunani cewa tsakanin jiki da ruhi ya zama muhimmanci ga lafiya.
Duk mu yi tunani da wahala game da wannan fahimta.
Tashar ta yi magana ne game da bayanin Salamis, wani yakin ruwa da ya faru fiye da shekara dubu biyar da suka wuce inda yan Grekawa da suka yi yawa suka yi nasara a kan sojojin Persiya mai tsanani.
A lokacin da horizons mu na rufe, yana da kusan vertigo-inducing don virtually shiga wani live audience a kallon (subtitled) live actors duk a Greece yayin da suke yin wani millenniums-old play.
Aeschylus ya kasance yana yin yaki a Salamis, amma fim din ya yi wani sako: Wannan mai shekaru a cikin nasara ya sa labarin nasa a cikin wadanda suka yi nasara, yana yin kallon da yake da jin dadi ga matsalolin da 'yan tawayen da ya yi yaki da su a kwanan nan.
A wata masu yara na Persiya, da suke da riguna da tsada da tsawon kuma da white button-down shirts, sun fara aiki.
Suna a birnin su na jiran labarin sarautar su Xerxes, wanda yake tare da Athens a yakin.
Enter Atossa, mahaifiyar Xerxes, wadda ta yi rasuwa, (Lydia Koniordou) a cikin rigar baki mai girma da take kama da wata kaya, ba ta kama da ita ba; ita ce mutum a cikin kayan jiki mai karfi, kuma mai karfi da kuma mai karfi.
Koniordou, wanda shine daga cikin mafi girma 'yan wasan fage a Greece, yana sani da aikin ciki ba tare da yin wani abu ba - tana shirya da kuma taka rawa a wani taron National Theater of Greece na "The Persians" da ya buga New York City Center a 2006 - kuma tana tabbatar da abubuwan da suke faru ba tare da yin wani abu ba.
Ya kasance mafi yawan lokuta, tana tsakiyar wurin taro na tsakiya, tana fitar da karfin zuciya da tashin hankali da yake nuna yadda abin ya faru da jami'an gida.
Tsoro da dukkan mutane ke ji ya tabbatar, cikin bayanai masu tsanani, ta wata sako (Argyris Pandazaras) daga kafar fada.
A cikin wani abin mamaki sosai, ya rera labarin yakin, yana kara kansa cikin mamaki yayin yaran chorus suke tafiya a kansa da kuma Giorgos Poulios score mai kama da drone ya karu zuwa wani abu da ya zama mai saurin saurin ji.
Sun karbi taimako daga Atossa mai matarsa ta rasu (Nikos Karathanos), wanda aka kira daga duniya ta kasa, da Xerxes (Argyris Xafis), wanda ya samu nasara ya tashi daga rushewa.
Ribobi a kan rigarsa na yana jikinsa suna nuna jini (Kayan kayan kwalliya na Eva Nathena suna taimaka sosai wajen labarun).
