Sekitari ya amince cewa yawan masu yawon shakatawa sun bar kansu ba da lokaci don canza ko sauya shirinsu.
Ya fahimce ni cewa wannan yana haifar da matsala ga waɗanda suke shiga cikin wannan a Spain ko waɗanda suka yi nazarin zuwa, amma dole ne mu iya daukar matakai masu sauri da karfi don kare Turai, ya ce.
