QB Herbert cikin 4 zaben da aka sanya suna da Chargers.
COSTA MESA, Calif. (AP) - Los Angeles Chargers sun karbi hudu daga cikin 'yan wasan da suka yi wa kamfanin rajista, ciki har da mai kwamfuta Justin Herbert, kuma sun yi amfani da sauran biyu daga cikin 'yan wasan da suka yi wa kamfanin rajista.
Chargers sun samu nasarar samun sakamakon aikace-aikacen da suka yi da kungiyar su ta karatu a ranar Asabar lokacin da suka zo taron koyarwa don aikin jiki da kayan aiki.
Tare da Herbert, wanda aka zaba da karba na biyar, an sanar da siyarwa da masu karba na waya Joe Reed (kashi na biyar) da KJ Hill (kashi na bakwai) tare da tsaro na kashi na shida Alohi Gilman.
Sun yarda da Kenneth Murray Jr., wanda aka zaba a farkon rana, da kuma Joshua Kelley, wanda aka zaba a rana ta hudu, sun yi amana da sharuɗɗa.
Herbert ya fara 42 wasanni a Oregon, yana samun nasara 29-13 tare da 10,541 da kuma 108 dukkanin layuka.
Ya jagoranci Ducks zuwa Championship na Pac-12 a shekarar da ta gabata, yana watsa 32 touchdowns da kuma 6 interceptions a cikin 14 wasanni.
Ya kammala shekaru da nasara a kan Wisconsin a cikin Rose Bowl, inda ya tsere guda uku da aka zaba shi a matsayin mai kyautar mai karfi.
Herbert zai yi kokarin takarawa da Tyrod Taylor mai shekaru da yawa don matsayin mai fara.
Chargers za su samu sabon mai kwastam bayan Philip Rivers ya tafi ta hanyar kyautar kashe kashe bayan shekaru 14 a matsayin mai fara.
Murray ya zama sakamakon 23 bayan Los Angeles suka yi hannun jari da New England don su sake shiga farkon rana.
Yana da zama wani uku-kungiyar Associated Press All-America zaɓi a bara bayan ya jagorar Sooners da 102 takalma, ciki har da 69 solo.
Kanye West ya ce zai iya yin nasara a kan Joe Biden "daga rubuta a cikin" - RT USA News
Daga bayan ya fitar da launin familinsa a kan Twitter, rap enigma Kanye West ya sake haifar da rayuwarsa a kan tambayar zai yi ko ba zai yi takarar shugabancin kasar, inda ya ce zai iya yin nasara a kan Joe Biden ta hanyar kawo kuri'u ta rubuta kawai.
Bayan sanar da sabuwar album da bayyana cewa ya kokarin aurewa matarsa Kim Kardashian na biyu shekaru, Kanye West ya sake kallon takarar shugabancin Amurka a 2020 a ranar Asabar, a sanarwar da ta ce "ZAN IYA TAFIYA BIDEN DA KARATUN KOMAI."
Idan West yana cikin tsananin son zama shugaban kasa, za a iya samun nasarar sa ne ta hanyar zabar da rubutu, ko kuma wani nau'i na nuna alamu.
Rapper ya sanar da nasa takarar a ranar 4 ga Yuli, bayan kammala lokacin da ya bukaci a yi aiki a matsayin takarar a kasashe goma sha biyar.
Duk da haka, West ya ci gaba da yin aiki kuma ya aika dokoki zuwa Komiyar Zaben Tarayya (FEC), kuma ya samu ya saka sunansa a kan kujeru a Oklahoma.
Yayin da ya wuce, ya gudanar da taron tsayawa daya, lokacin da ya magana ga jama'a da ke kwance a jakunkunan kare kai, yana bayar da maganarsa ba tare da mikon ba ko makon.
West ya fito da baya a kan sace-sace, yana kuka yayin da ya bayar da sako mai kyau ga Kirista, ya ce zai sa hanyar sadarwa ta gaya muku cewa "ina da wahala".
Kanye West ya ce ya yi kokarin aurenta Kim Kardashian, ya zargi ita da uwar miji ta "Kris Jong Un" da cin zarafi na mata baki daya.
Wannan yana da gaskiya, kuma taron West ya samu bayyana a cikin shafukan labarai da kuma jaridun gidan yanar gizo a matsayin wani aiki na yada labari, shaida na cutar zuciya, ko kuma duka biyu.
Duk da wani yankin bincike da aka yi a baya, West ya samu biyu cikin dari a kasa da kasa, yana kai tsaye da Jam'iyyar Libertarian ta Jo Jorgensen da kuma wani kashi da Jam'iyyar Green ta Howie Hawkins.
Yayin da yake yawan gaske ba zai iya kai Joe Biden da ya fi shahara 48 cikin 100 ba, a theory ya iya kashe kuri'u daga Biden don ganin shugaban Donald Trump ya samu zaben na biyu - wani abu da masu sharhi a dukkan bangarorin suka yi zaton zai zama shi plan.
North Korea ta sanar da yanayi na musamman bayan an samu rahoto na cutar Covid-19.
Shugaban kasar North Korea Kim Jong-un ya yi kira ga taron muhimmin politburo bayan da wani mutum da aka yi tsammanin ya kamu da cutar Covid-19 ya dawo daga kasar Kudu bayan ya yi shigar da kansa ta hanyar haram a wannan wata, rahotanni na kasar ta bayyana a ranar Lahadi.
Idan an tabbatar, zai zama karamin yaro na farko da aka yarda da shi da hukumomin kasar Korea ta Arewa, wadanda har yanzu sun ce kasar bata da wani yaro na tabbatar da cutar coronavirus.
Kim ya sanar da yanayin tashin hankali kuma ya yanke hukunci na kulle kofar birnin Kaesong, inda ya kira shi "yanayin muhimmanci inda cutar ta zama za ta shigo kasar," rahoton agenciyar sabbin labarai ta KCNA.
Daga bayanin KCNA, wani mutum da ya yi sace-sacen zuwa Koriya ta Kudu a shekara uku da suka wuce ya dawo ta yamma ta kasar da take tsakanin biyu da alamun da suka nuna cewa yana da cutar Covid-19.
"A ranar 19 ga watan Yuli, an samu wani abu mai tsanani a birnin Kaesong inda wani mai tafiya zuwa kudancin shekara uku da suka wuce, wanda aka zargi da ciwon cutar marar kyau ya dawo bayan ya yi kuskure ta yi kuskuren yin kwace kwace ta tsakanin iyaka," in ji KCNA.
KCNA ba ta bayyana ko wannan mutum ya yi aikin gwajin ba, amma ta ce an samu sakamako mai tsanani daga wasu gwaje-gwajen lafiya na fitar da sanyi daga kwayar haɗin kai ta wannan mutumin da kuma daga jini, wanda ya sa hukumomi su yi tsaron wannan mutumin da kuma bincika kowa da ya yi magana da shi.
North Korea ta samu kimanin kitso na gwaje-gwajen coronavirus daga Russia da sauran kasashe, kuma ta yi aikin rufe iyakoki da tsaurara.
Mutane da dama a cikin kasar da take tsare-tsare suna da kulle, amma an sauya tsare-tsaren da suka riga da shigo.
A cikin makonnin da suka gabata, Arewacin Korea ma ta kara yin kokarin yin korafi a kan masu barin Arewacin Korea zuwa Kudancin Korea a matsayin "mutane makami" kuma ta kira ga Kudancin Korea da ta yi wa kungiyoyin da ke aika sako da abinci zuwa Arewacin Korea.
Kim ya aiko da bincike akan jami'an tsaro a yankin iyaka inda aka yi zaton wannan mutum ya shiga don "yin hukunci mai tsanani da daukan matakan da ake bukata."
Paul Pogba ya bayyana alamunsa game da tafiyarsa bayan Man Utd ta kammala daukar wurin Champions League.
Manchester United star Paul Pogba ya bayyana cewa zai zauna a kungiyar nan wannan makon bayan Red Devils sun samu wuri a cikin jerin gaba daya.
Nasara ta kammala da nasara 2-0 a kan Leicester, wanda ya sa United ta kammala a sama na uku, a gaban Frank Lampard's Chelsea.
United sun kasance 14 points daga Leicester kawai 12 wasanni da suka wuce amma wani mai ban mamaki tashi na yanayi ya sa Red Devils su kammala a cikin hudu mafi girma.
Pogba ya kasance ake sa ran zai fita daga kungiyar wannan yanayi bayan ya nema ya fita biyu a cikin biyu da suka gabata shekaru.
Pandemiyar yana nufin cewa kananan kulob zasu yi kudi a wannan watan bazara, kuma babu mai sayarwa da zai iya hada kudin sayarwa da kudin albashin Pogba don kawo shi daga Old Trafford.
Wannan bayani ya taimaka wa Pogba a cikin watanni da suka gabata yayin da nashi nuna kansa, da kuma nashi aikin, suka kara inganta.
Kuma Faransan ya fitar da alamun da ya nuna cewa zai ci gaba da zama a kungiyar bayan ya wallafa a shafinsa na Instagram bayan nasarar da 'yan uwansa suka samu 2-0.
Pogba ya mayar da hankali ne a kan fara cin nasara da kungiyar ta sake shiga gasar, amma yawan masu biyan kuɗi suna ganin hakan ya nuna cewa zai ci gaba da zama a kungiyar lokacin da suke yin gasar tare da mafi kyawun kungiyoyin Turai.
Pogba yana da shekara daya zuwa karshe a kan yarjejeniyarsa da take gudana, duk da haka kungiyar za ta iya kara wannan da watanni 12, wanda hakan yana nufin cewa yana da shekaru biyu zuwa karshe.
United suna neman yin karin karfin Pogba's deal kuma suna neman sanin yanayinsa kafin mako mai zuwa.
Pogba, daga gare shi, yana jin dadi a kungiyar kuma an kara masa murna da zo da Bruno Fernandes.
Portuguese mai wasan kwaikwayo ya zo Old Trafford ya yi alfahari, kuma zuwansa ya baiwa Pogba damar yin wasa a matsayin mai karfi a tsakiyar tsakiya, wanda ya kara inganta yanayinsa.
